    • fetchAllSessionsAsync

      public static Map<String,Session> fetchAllSessionsAsync(Map<String,Session> previous)
      Gets all Session information asynchronously. Corresponds to GET '/api/sessions' with the hash parameter.
      Parameters:
      previous - Old session id to data Map.
      Returns:
      New session id to data Map.
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if previous is null.

    • getAllSessions

      public static Map<String,Session> getAllSessions()
      Gets all Session information synchronously. Corresponds to GET '/api/sessions' without the hash parameter.
      Returns:
      Session id to data Map.

    • addSessionFromSaveGame

      public static String addSessionFromSaveGame(String creator, String gameId, String saveGameId, String accessToken)
      Adds a new Session from a previously registered SaveGame. Corresponds to POST '/api/sessions'.
      Parameters:
      creator - Creator of the session.
      gameId - Game service id.
      saveGameId - Save game id.
      accessToken - Access token (UserRole.ROLE_PLAYER required).
      Returns:
      Session id.
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if creator, gameId, saveGameId or accessToken is null.

      public static Session fetchSessionAsync(String sessionId, Session previous)
      Gets a Session information asynchronously. Corresponds to GET '/api/sessions/{sessionId}' with the hash parameter.
      Parameters:
      sessionId - Session id.
      previous - Previous session data.
      Returns:

      Throws:

    • removeSession

      public static void removeSession(String sessionId, String accessToken)
      Deletes a Session. Corresponds to DELETE '/api/sessions/{sessionId}'.
      Parameters:
      sessionId - Session id.
      accessToken - Access token (UserRole.ROLE_ADMIN required, or the token owner is the creator of session).
      Throws:
      NullPointerException - if sessionId or accessToken is null.
